-ever-lived?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=top_boards_2014&utm_content=board_image\n\n\n** The Oldest Animals that Ever Lived\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nLinden Melvin\nhttp://learni.st/users/106194/boards/85179--must-see-moments-from-the-2014-world-cup?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=top_boards_2014&utm_content=board_image\n\n\n** Must-See Moments from the 2014 World Cup\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPatrick Weber\nhttp://learni.st/users/lauren.kelly/boards/83471-11-celebrities-famous-last-words?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=top_boards_2014&utm_content=board_image\n\n\n** 11 Celebrities' Famous Last Words\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nLauren Kelly\n\nCreate your own boards today!\n\nOn Learnist, we provide a platform that helps people share their knowledge. After all, the best way to learn is to teach others.\nShare your knowledge (http://learni.st/dashboard)\n\nGet your Learnist board featured on our homepage and promoted in our emails. Click Here (http://learni.st/users/shavers/boards/85499-how-to-get-featured-on-learnist?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=top_boards_2014&utm_content=link_text) to Learn More.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTry Learnist on your Android or iOS device\nhttps://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.learnist https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/learnist-worlds-knowledge/id826591175?mt=8&uo=4\n\nDon't want to receive email notifications? Adjust your message settings (<%= root_url %>email_preferences/<%= user ? user.guid : '' %>) .\n\nLearnist values your privacy and does not make your email address available to any other third party without your permission.\n\n\u00a9 2014, Learnist Inc. 500 3rd Street Suite 260, San Francisco, CA 94107\n\nThis email was sent to jeeproject@yahoo.com (mailto:jeeproject@y